These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
House: cape-cod, ranch-style, art-deco
1. the art-deco house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
2. the art-deco house is between the cape-cod house and the ranch-style house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| House   | cape-cod | art-deco | ranch-style |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, bird, ferret
1. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the ferret##2
2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Pet   | ferret | cat | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: onion, plum, cherry
1. the person eating plum is between the person eating onion and the person eating cherry##2
2. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Food   | cherry | plum | onion |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, montecristo, dunhill
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is between the montecristo-smoker and the cain-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Cigar   | cain | dunhill | montecristo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: tomato, watermelon, pepper
1. the person eating tomato is between the person eating pepper and the person eating watermelon##2
2. the person eating pepper is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Food   | watermelon | tomato | pepper |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-6::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, august, november
1. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in june##2
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2    |      3      |
| Birthday   | august | november | june |

 #################################

 
